description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the live September match up between The Pirates and The Goddesses.
All four of these girls are former collegiate athletes. All are as fit and ripped as the day they graduated. All four are looking for their first win in this year's super competitive Tag Team League.
The Pirates are led by this year's Summer Vengeance Champion Dia Zerva. Looking for their first win of the year, they see the underpowered Goddesses and expect to dish out some pain.
The Goddesses have the two most fit and ripped wrestlers on the roster. They are the smallest team in the league, however their endurance and strength are unmatched. This team is fast, light and brutal.
The first round was action-packed and rough as it gets. Both teams locked in punishing submission holds but no one ever broke. After 12 minutes and 6 tags in, only a few points separated these two teams going into the locker room.
title: ROUND ONE: The Pirates(0-3) vs The Goddesses(0-2)
